BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Movement & Exercise) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Regular moderate exercise reduces inflammatory markers. Aim for 150 minutes per week of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (moderate activity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (- Walking: 30 minutes daily, preferably in nature) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (- Yoga: Reduces cortisol and inflammation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.2 Td (- Swimming: Low-impact, full-body movement) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.2 Td (- Strength training: 2-3x per week, moderate intensity) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.2 Td (- Avoid overtraining: Excessive exercise increases inflammation) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 542.4 Td (Sleep Optimization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (Poor sleep dramatically increases inflammation. Prioritize 7-9 hours nightly.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 510.4 Td (- Consistent sleep/wake schedule \(even weekends\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.4 Td (- Dark, cool bedroom \(65-68F\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482.4 Td (- No screens 1 hour before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 468.4 Td (- Magnesium before bed may help) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 454.4 Td (- Address sleep apnea if suspected) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 424.6 Td (Stress Management) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 406.6 Td (Chronic stress is one of the biggest drivers of inflammation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 392.6 Td (- Daily meditation or deep breathing \(10+ minutes\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 378.6 Td (- Time in nature \(reduces cortisol\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 364.6 Td (- Social connection and community) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 350.6 Td (- Journaling and gratitude practice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 336.6 Td (- Set boundaries and reduce overcommitment) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 306.8 Td (Supplements to Discuss with Your Doctor) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 288.8 Td (- Omega-3 fish oil \(EPA/DHA\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 274.8 Td (- Curcumin \(turmeric extract with piperine\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 260.8 Td (- Vitamin D3 \(most people are deficient\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 246.8 Td (- Probiotics \(for gut health\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 232.8 Td (- Magnesium glycinate) Tj ET
