stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: How quickly will I see results?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Most people notice improvements in energy and digestion within 2-3 weeks. Significant) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (reduction in pain and inflammation markers may take 6-12 weeks of consistent dietary) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (changes.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Q: Do I have to give up all inflammatory foods forever?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (No. The goal is an 80/20 approach - eat anti-inflammatory foods 80% of the time.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (Occasional treats won't undo your progress if your baseline diet is solid.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 546.6 Td (Q: Can I still drink coffee?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (Yes! Coffee in moderation \(1-3 cups\) is actually anti-inflammatory due to its polyphenol) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (content. Avoid adding sugar and artificial creamers.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 488.8 Td (Q: What about nightshade vegetables?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (Nightshades \(tomatoes, peppers, eggplant\) are anti-inflammatory for most people. Only) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (eliminate them if you notice they trigger YOUR symptoms.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 431.0 Td (Q: Is organic food necessary?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 415.0 Td (Prioritize organic for the Dirty Dozen \(thin-skinned produce\). For other items,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 401.0 Td (conventional is fine - eating vegetables matters more than organic vs conventional.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 373.2 Td (Q: Can this diet help autoimmune conditions?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 357.2 Td (Many people with autoimmune conditions report significant improvement with) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 343.2 Td (anti-inflammatory diets. Work with your doctor to complement medical treatment.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 315.4 Td (Q: How much water should I drink?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 299.4 Td (Aim for half your body weight in ounces daily. Hydration supports every anti-inflammatory) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 285.4 Td (process in your body.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 257.6 Td (Q: What if I have food allergies?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 241.6 Td (Adapt the meal plan around your allergies. The principles remain the same - focus on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 227.6 Td (whole, colorful, unprocessed foods.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 199.8 Td (Q: Should I take anti-inflammatory supplements?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 183.8 Td (Food should be your foundation. Discuss supplements with your healthcare provider,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 169.8 Td (especially omega-3s, vitamin D, and curcumin.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 142.0 Td (Q: Can children follow this diet?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 126.0 Td (The principles are healthy for all ages. Adjust portions and ensure adequate calories for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 112.0 Td (growing children. Consult a pediatrician.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
